dc_title_s: Carte de l'Egypte, de la Nubie, de l'Abissinie &c.; Par Guillaume De Lisle.
dc_description_s: Relief shown pictorially. Engraved by Desrosiers. 87 written on upper right corner of sheet. 1 map: hand col.; 48 x 59 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
